        "tag": "p",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Quick to notice details of your environment, you gain the following benefits:"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "element",
        "tag": "ul",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "element",
            "tag": "li",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "Increase your Intelligence or Wisdom score by 1, to a maximum of 20."
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "element",
        "tag": "ul",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "element",
            "tag": "li",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "If you can see a creature's mouth while it is speaking a language you understand, you can interpret what it's saying by reading its lips."
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "element",
        "tag": "ul",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "element",
            "tag": "li",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "You have a +5 bonus to your passive Wisdom (Perception) and passive Intelligence (Investigation) scores."
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      }
    ],
    "html": "<div id=\"page-content\">\n<p>Source: Player's Handbook</p>\n<p>Quick to notice details of your environment, you gain the following benefits:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Increase your Intelligence or Wisdom score by 1, to a maximum of 20.</li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n<li>If you can see a creature's mouth while it is speaking a language you understand, you can interpret what it's saying by reading its lips.</li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n<li>You have a +5 bonus to your passive Wisdom (Perception) and passive Intelligence (Investigation) scores.</li>\n</ul>\n</div>"
